Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.86,0:01:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.23,0:01:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空易拉罐要扔進垃圾箱！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(title)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.80,0:01:55.80,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.63,0:02:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請留步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是可疑人物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,軌道用於通行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,規則用來遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}註：軌道（レール）和規則（ルール）在日語中發音相近
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人稱佛朗明哥武士就是我！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以亂丟垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？但是這裡可是垃圾場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}垃圾和可回收垃圾的分類及回收日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs32}諮詢電話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}可燃垃圾 週五、二
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}不可燃垃圾 週四
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}可回收垃圾 週三
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}塑料垃圾 週一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}大型垃圾 每月第2個星期一
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs40}*請務必遵守
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.16,0:02:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在還沒到週五！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.45,0:02:36.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太斤斤計較了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不 規定就是這樣寫的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小哥你能幫我扔垃圾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.85,0:02:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早上起不來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.71,0:02:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.67,0:02:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等 等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.26,0:02:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 第二天早上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.47,0:02:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那袋垃圾就被放在了我家門前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.85,0:03:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您覺得是那位小哥放的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.81,0:03:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回頭想想 那小哥搞不好是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.48,0:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扮得怪裡怪氣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還說自己是什麼武士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近確實有人反映這類情況
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.63,0:03:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是一到晚上就有個穿著全身緊身衣的男人到處亂晃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還自稱是「正義的夥伴」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.70,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫什麼來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.60,0:03:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.40,0:03:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是叫「佛朗明哥武士」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個 好嚇人啊 快抓住他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 他也沒做什麼壞事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 丟垃圾請按時間來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒誒？一般都會那樣丟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.75,0:03:43.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般來說確實都會這樣丟呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你吃過飯了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正打算去買
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.53,0:04:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼到我家一起吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.36,0:04:03.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有咖喱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.80,0:04:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你家也就只有咖喱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這掛件真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.71,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便拿別人的東西可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼會做那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.14,0:04:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 難道是你女朋友的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般都不會扔的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是晚上扔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.83,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貓和烏鴉會把垃圾吃得到處都是的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.33,0:04:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用網罩住不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生你壓根不懂飢餓的貓和烏鴉有多麼兇猛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.08,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們是野獸 是畜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是一樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.19,0:04:46.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 我們已經陸續收到了當地居民的投訴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.99,0:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義活動也要適可而止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.90,0:04:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我並沒有朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了後藤先生以外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.79,0:05:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別補充說明了 真噁心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.28,0:05:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.23,0:05:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些資料我忘了給你 所以就帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.62,0:05:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.24,0:05:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是石原小姐 我的經紀人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.27,0:05:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐很討厭這種興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她發現的話我就死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就在門口打發她走唄
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.40,0:05:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能趕她走 因為這裡的租金基本上都是公司出的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.81,0:05:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.00,0:05:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也有出一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我打算爭取有一天全部自己承擔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.26,0:05:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快幫忙！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 好…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.46,0:05:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.27,0:05:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 突然造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:54.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:01.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.24,0:06:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.45,0:06:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只在你搬進這裡的時候來過一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.73,0:06:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒搞得亂七八糟的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.45,0:06:09.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.96,0:06:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羽佐間的經紀人 名叫石原
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫後藤
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生是位警察
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.82,0:06:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 警察？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.57,0:06:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.86,0:06:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恕我冒昧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問你和羽佐間是在哪認識的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.97,0:06:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 因為我也住在這一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:32.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.07,0:06:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我先告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟打擾你們就不太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.09,0:06:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她確實很有魄力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.28,0:06:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生起氣來真的很可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼再見了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.03,0:06:56.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.59,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事電話聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.08,0:07:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先 把麥克遞給主唱麻里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.67,0:07:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.61,0:07:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.70,0:07:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,間奏的時候你還要再出場一次
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.37,0:07:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微跳兩下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就跳一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.07,0:07:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會跳舞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那部分能不能找個替身來…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別自以為是了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.86,0:07:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為工作人員花了多少工夫才拿下這份工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.44,0:07:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的你只不過是個滿大街都是的普通帥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:31.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後好不容易才有了一丁丁點名氣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.84,0:07:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後是成為大牌還是被人像滯銷商品一樣叫賣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.16,0:07:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就看你現在 看你現在怎麼表現了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.69,0:07:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該知道你現在的待遇很優厚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:44.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這說明公司對你非常看好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.81,0:07:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可別辜負我們的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:47.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知 知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.13,0:07:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:53.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我們從頭再過一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.69,0:08:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼呢 快過來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺和雜誌的拍攝完全不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.48,0:08:08.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.01,0:08:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用緊張也沒事 因為今天的主角是MMM
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.99,0:08:14.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不過就是個群眾演員
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:16.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:20.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 你也要爭取給觀眾留下一點印象
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mineral Miracle Muses 入場
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.88,0:08:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.37,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.07,0:08:34.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.25,0:08:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.55,0:08:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你當這是選舉拉票啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就請多多關照了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.68,0:08:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:49.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人不不不才請多多包涵！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:51.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.12,0:08:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那小哥是咋回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是樹工作室的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的名片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.36,0:09:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是經營新聞網站「HIGH ROLLERS HI!」的今野
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.80,0:09:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Caesar Pro的石原 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:14.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是Caesar的人啊 今天是為何到場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來陪同我司藝人羽佐間的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.19,0:09:18.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.57,0:09:20.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個英俊小夥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.39,0:09:24.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐也很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.12,0:09:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生走到舞台中央打開盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後麻里拿起麥克風
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.36,0:09:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一段我們來排練一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:33.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.80,0:09:34.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生 你太僵硬了點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.85,0:09:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這只是彩排 所以放輕鬆點 好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.53,0:09:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.75,0:09:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生 放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.50,0:09:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今野先生 你不用到樹工作室那邊看看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必擔心 我已經和他們約好拍攝結束後進行採訪了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.80,0:09:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石原小姐稍後有什麼打算嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:02.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 羽佐間正義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.38,0:10:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的危機 英雄應該能輕易克服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始彩排
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.44,0:10:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄應該能…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:12.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 如果是紅斧戰士就一定沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.92,0:10:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 開始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.29,0:10:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}擊碎世間的一切邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生 走出來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.05,0:10:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用盡全力將它劈成兩半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.79,0:10:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}將謊言築起的罪惡都市
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.55,0:10:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}一刀兩斷 正義的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.15,0:10:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}百發百中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生 打開盒子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.28,0:10:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 麻里 拿起它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}鮮紅的巨斧雄偉矗立
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.95,0:10:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用巨斧斬盡邪惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.43,0:10:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}用巨斧劈開黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.73,0:10:54.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羽佐間先生 關上盒子 退場
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻里 戴上麥克風唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.15,0:10:58.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Kill and break! Kill and break!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}其名曰 紅斧戰士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛剛…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.24,0:11:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停 停！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:15.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 麻里？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.31,0:11:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重頭來一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(part-b)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.13,0:12:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他突然衝出來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趴在了地上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.11,0:12:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要偷看我的內褲！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 關於那個緊身衣男的舉報多起來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他絕對是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快想點辦法處理他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.92,0:12:26.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:28.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我和別人約在這兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.51,0:12:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你淋濕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是騎自行車來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下著雨還騎車？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.10,0:12:38.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是騎自行車也很不錯的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.34,0:12:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我很快就熟悉了這一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.10,0:12:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.99,0:12:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝 謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.68,0:12:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定好要喝什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.36,0:12:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.76,0:12:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 你不喝酒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.19,0:12:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:12:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才19歲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:12:59.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:05.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫時別再扮佛朗明哥武士了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？ 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.50,0:13:12.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說過了吧 有人來投訴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是晚上有穿著緊身衣的變態出沒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是正義的夥伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.72,0:13:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點別人沒理解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.21,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你前天也被人錯當成變態了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是悲傷的誤會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是誤會解決不了問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.20,0:13:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.41,0:13:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一杯生啤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:32.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 別再扮佛朗明哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否則我真的會抓你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛的台詞 很有特攝片的風格呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 我可不是開玩笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.16,0:13:44.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我扮英雄也是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.35,0:13:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.39,0:13:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.77,0:13:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你並不是在和邪惡戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.10,0:13:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在製造麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:14:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道亂丟東西 提前扔垃圾這種事不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.28,0:14:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不會一一去治理 因為這種事太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事是不會根絕的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.38,0:14:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,警察說這話合適嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.36,0:14:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合適啊 因為我正視現實
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是 如果只是要提醒別人注意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.91,0:14:15.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的本來面目不就行了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.40,0:14:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒙著個臉 不覺得很狡猾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.49,0:14:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做是因為考慮到今後的發展
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後什麼發展？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碰上罪犯 黑社會或者邪惡軍團的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.30,0:14:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是暴露身份就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.74,0:14:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我們警察的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點權力都沒有的你來插手反而更麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.45,0:14:40.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底 你憑什麼指責別人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.92,0:14:43.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你就一件虧心事都沒做過？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.62,0:14:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.40,0:14:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不打傘的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛聽說過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學一年級的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一個雨天 我打算回家的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻發現我的傘不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:12.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我實在沒轍 就打著別人的傘回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事很普遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 班上的內田同學請假了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為淋著雨回家而感冒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和爺爺一起去道歉 看到病倒的內田同學的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.33,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我意識到自己做的事就是犯罪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.02,0:15:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘是日本被盜數量最多的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為突然降雨而將別人的傘「借走」的人不在少數
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被偷走傘的人又會擅自拿走別人的傘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.93,0:15:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不過就是把傘」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.38,0:15:51.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這種意識在製造犯罪的連鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.32,0:15:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罪惡就在人們的不知不覺間滋長！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:58.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你就不打傘了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.67,0:16:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也太大驚小怪了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.46,0:16:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕這樣的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.62,0:16:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓我在某個同樣的雨天再次犯下偷傘的罪過
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.43,0:16:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的我倒也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:13.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你這論點太極端了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盜傘這種事已經成為社會體系的一部分了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.49,0:16:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.73,0:16:21.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就更應該一點點地去改變這個社會嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.11,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘是否重要 不是應該由傘的主人來決定嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是500日元的塑料傘 也不應該去偷啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.40,0:16:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說你要做就低調點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要扮成佛朗明哥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.56,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您叫我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.03,0:16:38.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蘇打酒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烏龍茶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.98,0:16:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生 要打烊了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.87,0:16:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經結完賬了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.16,0:16:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我們先出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:16:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真別再扮佛朗明哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個問題我們改天再聊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.28,0:17:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝惠顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘沒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是你女朋友的傘吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.20,0:17:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 是她忘在我這的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.05,0:17:17.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:23.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個混帳！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅燈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.73,0:17:35.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把傘還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.39,0:17:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.54,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生 請交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.16,0:17:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.03,0:18:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘 傘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘 傘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.98,0:18:40.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.19,0:18:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在這
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.21,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改為B計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,換回路線A
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.64,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說垃圾要早上扔！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,躲開！ 躲開！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.82,0:19:29.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘 傘 傘
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把傘…請把傘還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.96,0:19:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傘？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.21,0:20:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把傘不是你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請你歸還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也被人拿走了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.32,0:20:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上沒有可以隨便偷的傘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.87,0:20:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把傘還給我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.71,0:20:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我們去抓偷你傘的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你要打電話讓我看這段視頻？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.74,0:20:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是覺得很有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得他的聲音很像羽佐間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.92,0:20:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.79,0:20:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有工作 先掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.90,0:20:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}好 我們去抓偷你傘的傢伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.03,0:20:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是點擊率在一週內達到了9萬次的熱門視頻
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.89,0:20:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 這位英雄叫什麼名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次登場的羽佐間先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:53.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佛朗明哥武士
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.76,0:20:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別猜對啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(ED)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ランプシェードが頭に被さり
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,私に目隠ししたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,シャツのボタンの穴から
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君を感じれるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妄想伝えてるサイチュー
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,君が行くよとサイン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,車の助手席乗れば
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:29.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,発車音 胸の音みたいにキュルルン
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:35.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんどんスキになっていい？君の事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:42.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,横顔だけで受け流す君は草食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冗談ばかりの会話も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:51.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今はマジなloving you message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次は、ドコドコへ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:00.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余裕綽々な君のリードに
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人感じてノックダウン
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:10.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,どんどんアイしちゃっていい？君の事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:17.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赤信号でキスせがむ私 肉食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,このまま終われないデートタイム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:26.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baby love, イエスを聞かせて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:03.80,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈罩蓋過頭頂
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.82,0:21:06.70,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遮住了我的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.13,0:21:10.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從襯衫鈕扣的縫隙裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.14,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感知到你的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.55,0:21:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在傳遞妄想之時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.80,0:21:19.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你作出啟程的示意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.97,0:21:22.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乘上副駕駛座
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.18,0:21:29.21,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只聽引擎聲如心跳怦怦作響
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.57,0:21:35.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能越來越為你傾倒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.93,0:21:42.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只憑側臉悄然迴避的你難道是草食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:45.33,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不著邊際的玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.56,0:21:51.76,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今儼然已是真正的情話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:55.13,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你從容制定計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.19,0:22:00.94,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將我步步引導
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,週身散發的成熟將我攻陷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.78,0:22:10.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是否能越來越愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.19,0:22:17.18,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁紅燈之機索吻的我難道是肉食系？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:20.59,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不終結的約會時光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.75,0:22:26.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Baby love, 讓我聽到肯定的回答
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(epilogue)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你知道啊 羽佐間先生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.44,0:22:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為那9萬次裡有206次是我貢獻的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:37.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.43,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會看那麼多遍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.77,0:22:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅斧——戰士！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:45.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是下意識地點了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.54,0:22:45.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\bord2\shad3\4a&H00&\fs44\i1\pos(592,110)\4c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H7ABEE4&\c&H4F5D5D&}驚歎 英雄在夜晚的街道上現身！？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(next title)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:50.05,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真假佛朗明哥對決
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:54.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生為什麼會想當巡警呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是有部講葛飾區的巡警的漫畫嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.26,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs36}註：捏他「這裡是葛飾區龜有公園前派出所」 少年JUMP的最長連載作品
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:22:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.65,0:23:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是因為我小時候看了那部漫畫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.04,0:23:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那部漫畫那麼早就有了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.05,0:23:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 一直都有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.53,0:23:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看了之後就覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.77,0:23:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巡警可以佩槍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.66,0:23:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以上班拼模型看漫畫 所以很嚮往
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:17.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,後藤先生 那是漫畫裡才會有的設定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.01,0:23:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是說你有資格說這話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:21.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有你絕對沒資格說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.50,0:23:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在想來 那個人大概就是我的英雄吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.11,0:23:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現實地想 那個人已經超越了完美的範疇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起啊…喂 為什麼這一點上偏偏現實起來了！